data.description: Tucked away within the 2,000-acre forested master planned community of Woodlands Hills, sits the beautiful one-story, 128 Winged Elm Court! This spacious 3B/2B offers an open-concept floor with soaring ceilings, inviting floor plan with many upgrades, and enhanced landscape on the front and back. Enjoy cooking in your kitchen with extended cabinet/countertop space, gas cooktop, and large island overlooking into the Living Room and back yard as the kids play. Owners may enjoy their Master Bathroom upgraded walk-in shower or the flex room that can turn into you personal study/office space. Lastly, Reap the benefits from their NEWLY added luxury water softener system! This home sits on a cul-de-sac street and the amenities include a 17 acre Village Park with Bike Lanes, Splash Pads, Play Grounds, Dog Parks, Tennis Courts, Resort Style Pool with Event Center, and Fitness Center! Living just minutes away from I-45, Medical Centers, Shopping and Fine Dining, this property is quite the gem!
